### Local Testing Mode
### Set to true to use tests/config/ and tests/backups/ for local testing with mock SSH devices
### Set to false for production with real SSH devices
###
### When KIWISSH_LOCAL_TEST_MODE=true:
###   - Config from: tests/config/
###   - Device sources from: tests/config/sources/devices.csv
###   - Backups saved to: tests/backups/
###
### When KIWISSH_LOCAL_TEST_MODE=false:
###   - Config from: config/
###   - Device sources from: config/sources/devices.csv
###   - Backups saved to: backups/ (in project root, next to config/)
###
KIWISSH_LOCAL_TEST_MODE=true

### API Configuration (optional)
# KIWISSH_API_PORT=8000
# KIWISSH_DEBUG=true

### Timezone Configuration (optional)
## Set timezone for logs and timestamps. Use IANA timezone format (e.g., Europe/Berlin, UTC, America/New_York)
## If not set, defaults to UTC. Database timestamps are always stored in UTC regardless of this setting.
TZ=Europe/Berlin
